eqlExtErrorTable.name: eqlExtErrorTable
eqlExtErrorTable.description: A conceptual table which associates extended error information with each SNMP operation that produced an error where such information is available

eqlExtErrorEntry.name: eqlExtErrorEntry
eqlExtErrorEntry.description: A sequence of extended error information for each SNMP operation producing an extended error

eqlEntIpAddr.name: eqlEntIpAddr
eqlEntIpAddr.description: The IP address of the entity making the SNMP request

eqlSNMPrid.name: eqlSNMPrid
eqlSNMPrid.description: The value of the request id of the SNMP PDU which resulted in the associated error.

eqlSNMPExtErrCode.name: eqlSNMPExtErrCode
eqlSNMPExtErrCode.description: The value of the extended error code resulting from the SNMP PDU with the associated request id and source address

eqlSNMPExtErrMsg.name: eqlSNMPExtErrMsg
eqlSNMPExtErrMsg.description: The human-readable, meaningful error message that is associated with the extended error code. In most cases, this will be identical to the string that appeared on the management console after the error occured
